        "tokens": [
          {
            "text": "在“计步数据追踪与位置服务”场景中，"
          },
          {
            "text": "我们会从用户授权状态、计步器传感器 (PEDOMETER)、地理位置信息 (Location)、本地存储配置收集"
          },
          {
            "text": "计步器传感器数据 (PEDOMETER)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_b6ae04dee5",
              "flowId": "flow:p1",
              "nodeId": "p1:n7"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "、"
          },
          {
            "text": "地理位置名称 (placeName)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_b6ae04dee5",
              "flowId": "flow:p1",
              "nodeId": "p1:n8"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "、"
          },
          {
            "text": "用户设定的步数目标 (stepGoal)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_b6ae04dee5",
              "flowId": "flow:p1",
              "nodeId": "p1:n9"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "和"
          },
          {
            "text": "错误日志信息 (Error Log Messages)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_b6ae04dee5",
              "flowId": "flow:p3",
              "nodeId": "p3:n7"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "，用于记录用户步数、提供运动状态反馈及基于位置的上下文展示。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "featureId": "ui_HomePage_125bb29ec1",
        "tokens": [
          {
            "text": "在“用户点击开始/停止按钮控制计步服务启停时，应用会收集用户的实时位置信息和运动步数数据，用于界面展示和后台持续追踪”场景中，"
          },
          {
            "text": "我们会从设备传感器（计步器）、GPS/定位服务收集"
          },
          {
            "text": "当前步数 (currentSteps)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_125bb29ec1",
              "flowId": "flow:p28",
              "nodeId": "p28:n3"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "、"
          },
          {
            "text": "起始位置 (startPosition)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_125bb29ec1",
              "flowId": "flow:p28",
              "nodeId": "p28:n4"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "和"
          },
          {
            "text": "当前位置 (currentLocation)",
            "jumpTo": {
              "featureId": "ui_HomePage_125bb29ec1",
              "flowId": "flow:p28",
              "nodeId": "p28:n5"
            }
          },
          {
            "text": "，用于在首页展示用户当前的运动步数和地理位置信息，支持用户手动开启或关闭后台计步任务。"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "featureId": "__app_permissions",
        "tokens": []
